mil3.4.9:0.1_0: The Simile of the Making Hand
mil3.4.9:1.3_0: “Great king, they don’t believe in any things that should be developed, but they completely understand extinguishment. Though those things should be given up, they realize extinguishment in the present life, and realize extinguishment.”
mil3.4.9:3.1_0: The ninth with quenching of quenching.
